Paṭiccavāra
Paccayapaccanīya
Saṅkhyāvāra
Suddha
15.
1464Nahetuyā dve, naārammaṇe pañca, naadhipatiyā cha, naanantare pañca, nasamanantare pañca, naaññamaññe pañca, naupanissaye pañca, napurejāte satta, napacchājāte nava, naāsevane satta, nakamme tīṇi, navipāke nava, naāhāre ekaṃ, naindriye ekaṃ, najhāne ekaṃ, namagge ekaṃ, nasampayutte pañca, navippayutte tīṇi, nonatthiyā pañca, novigate pañca. (Evaṃ gaṇetabbaṃ.)
1465Paccanīyaṃ.
